<H3> <TI>   Ren Jianxin Meets Uruguay Court Delegation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1301132094 Beijing XINHUA in English 1251 GMT 13 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1301132094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, January 13 (XINHUA) -- On behalf of the 
Chinese Supreme People's Court President Ren Jianxin, Gao 
Changli, vice-president of the court, met with and hosted a 
banquet here this evening in honor of Dr. Jorge Angel Marabotto 
Lugaro, president of the Supreme Court of Uruguay. 
  At the invitation of the Chinese Supreme People's Court, the 
four-member Uruguayan delegation arrived here January 12. They 
are also scheduled to visit Nanjing and Shanghai. 

