<H3> <TI>   Shandong Executes Three Train Robbers </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2801082294 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2801082294 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Criminals Liu Huishuang, Wu Henglong, and Tang 
Shanyou, who willfully committed armed robbery of train 
passengers, were sentenced to death and executed immediately by 
Jinan Railway Transportation Intermediate Court at Jinan Railway 
Station on 27 January. 

