<H3> <TI>   Hubei To Crack Down on Pornography, Hooliganism </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK0102095894 Wuhan Hubei People's Radio Network in Mandarin 
1000 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0102095894 </F>
<F P=104>  Wuhan Hubei People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Yesterday morning, the provincial party 
committee and government jointly held a broadcast teleconference 
at which they discussed major problems of Hubei's publications 
market and planned a province-wide crackdown on pornography and 
hooliganism during the Lunar New Year Festival period. 
  The provincial party committee and government decided to 
unfold a two-month crackdown on pornography and hooliganism 
across the province during the Lunar New Year Festival period 
with a view to resolving problems on Hubei's publications 
market. [passage omitted] 
  Provincial Vice Governor Han Nanpeng briefed the conference 
participants on major problems in Hubei's publications market 
and made arrangements for the upcoming province-wide crackdown. 
  Wang Zhongnong, provincial party committee standing 
committee 
member and propaganda department director, laid down 
requirements for the upcoming provincewide crackdown, saying: 
Under the new situation, we should heighten understanding of 
the importance, urgency, and complexity of the struggle against 
pornography and hooliganism. Under no circumstances should we 
try to seek economic growth at the expense of cultural growth. 
We should properly handle relations between the central task of 
economic construction and the struggle against pornography and 
hooliganism, between building a socialist market economy and 
opposing pornography and hooliganism, as well as between 
building two civilizations and opposing pornography and 
hooliganism. We should view the publications market from a 
high, political, and strategic plane, and strive to push ahead 
with the struggle against pornography and hooliganism with 
perfect assurance. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

