<F P=100> North Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hebei Firecracker Plant Accident Reveals Child Labor </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK0102042394 Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK0102042394 </F>
<F P=104>  Shijiazhuang Hebei People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An tremendous explosion took place at a firecracker 
plant in (Nanwangzhuang) Village of Longyao County on 29 
January. The provincial and city departments concerned have 
attached great importance to this. In the past two days, 
several units, including the provincial education commission and 
the provincial public security department, and leaders of 
Xingtai city, respectively went to the scene of the accident to 
help deal with the aftermath of the accident. 
  Longyao County has allocated over 80,000 yuan to save the 
wounded. 
  It is reported that (Wang Zongkun), director of the plant; 
and (Wang Rongen) and (Zhang Haibing), primary school teachers 
who had forced pupils to work at the plant, have been arrested 
for investigations by the security organ. 
  As of 2100 on 31 January when station reporter (Yang 
Jingzhou) released this report, over 30 pupils were saved from 
death by all-out rescue efforts, but the majority of them were 
unable to speak and were still unconsciousness. 

</TEXT>

