<H3> <TI>   Russian Foreign Minister Kozyrev Visits Xian </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK0302050094 Xian Shaanxi People's Radio Network in Mandarin 
0010 GMT 30 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0302050094 </F>
<F P=104>  Xian Shaanxi People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vice Governor Wang Shuangxi met Russian Foreign 
Minister Kozyrev and his entourage at the Xian Hotel yesterday 
afternoon. On behalf of the provincial government, Vice 
Governor Wang Shuangxi warmly welcomed Kozyrev and his 
entourage. After meeting him, Vice Governor Wang Shuangxi held 
a banquet in honor of the Russian guests. Russian Foreign 
Minister Kozyrev and his entourage arrived in Xian from Beijing 
yesterday afternoon. 

</TEXT>

