<F P=103> OW0202120194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, February 2 (XINHUA) -- An agreement on a 
government commodity loan to be provided by China to Georgia was 
signed here today. 
  Shi Guangsheng, Chinese vice-minister of foreign trade and 
economic co-operation, and visiting Georgian Vice-Minister of 
Finance Mirian Murjigleli [name as received] signed the 
agreement. 
  Murjigleli and his party arrived here on January 29. 

</TEXT>

